zapier.com.data:
[{"query":"query ThickServiceQuery($isPublic: Boolean!, $isUpcoming: Boolean) {
  services(isPublic: $isPublic, isUpcoming: $isUpcoming) {
    ...ServiceCategoryParts
    ...ServiceIdentificationParts
    ...ServiceMetadataParts
    ...ServiceActionMetadata
    __typename
  }
}

fragment ServiceCategoryParts on Service {
  categories {
    id: slug
    name
    slug
    __typename
  }
  __typename
}

fragment ServiceIdentificationParts on Service {
  id
  key: id
  name
  slug
  __typename
}

fragment ServiceMetadataParts on Service {
  ageInDays
  authType
  hasUpfrontFields
  isBeta
  isBuiltIn
  isDeprecated
  isFeatured
  isHidden
  isPremium
  isPublic
  isInvite
  isUpcoming
  popularity
  primaryColor
  __typename
}

fragment ServiceActionMetadata on Service {
  description
  hasFilters
  hasReads
  hasSearches
  hasSearchesOrWrites
  hasWrites
  __typename
}
","variables":{"isPublic":true,"isUpcoming":false,"__enableSentryLogging":true,"__cacheQuery":true},"operationName":"ThickServiceQuery"}]
